  "title": "Software Engineer Intern",
  "description": "<p><strong>Internship Period: May to December 2026 (minimum commitment period of 4–6 months)</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>The intern would be engaged in a variety of job tasks, including but not limited to:</p><ul><li>Document the existing process for the current internal system.</li><li>Partner with support to create a mobile app for internal maintenance using a rapid development platform.</li><li>Transition the existing internal maintenance web portal to a new platform.</li><li>Maintain the existing maintenance web portal, adding new features and performing bug fixes based on reported issues and team discussions.</li><li>Build new applications according to evolving business needs.</li><li>Integrate new applications with different internal and external systems.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Must be able to commit for 5 full work days.</li><li>Familiarity with Node.js development will be an advantage.</li><li>Ability to learn quickly and adapt to changing business requirements.</li><li>Good communication and documentation skills.</li></ul>",
